data.description: Range priced $399K to $425K. Nicely appointed home on a corner lot with pool and spa. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home offers a large great room and 2 additional dens that can be used for office space or made into additional bedrooms. One of the flex rooms is currently used as a 4th bedroom. The kitchen features wall to wall cabinets, granite counters, a center island breakfast bar, eat-in dining area, and steps out onto a covered patio. The backyard is fully-landscaped with pool, hot tub, storage shed, artificial grass, newer irrigation system and more! Home is outfitted with R39 insulation throughout, including garage. AC replaced in 2020. Solar panels are a 6Kv system (purchased by loan). Come. See. Stay!
